     As of today I can still hit a moving target more accurate than a still target. Why? I have no idea, I find a challenge in a moving one and boredom in a still figure.<br>
     Anyway, noone should have to kill a fellow American, simply and plain.<br>
     But as the school shootings, post office shootings, airport shootings, resturants and so forth and so on, we are wiping out the American people.  We need no help in killing us, the foreign countries should just stand back and watch us destroy ourselves.<br>
     We dont need hard and tough gun laws. Hell anyone is able to get a gun without registering it. They think they can stop that, hell the government hasnt stopped drugs yet.<br>
     Let's put every child at the age of 16 yrs into Boot Camp and teach them who the enemy is and it isnt their fellow American.<br>
